1. Make a heap (min or max).  Your out put should print the array before heapify and then after heapify. 
2. From the heap you make in step 1, use heapsort to sort the array.
In C++
Please run the program intuitively in Visual Studio 2015. This program includesfiles: Heap sort.cpp

First step, build max-heap by heapify function. Then do the heap sort.
